    "description": "<div style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;font-size:16px;line-height:1.6;color:#222;max-width:800px;margin:0 auto\" vocab=\"https://schema.org/\" typeof=\"Product\">\n  <div style=\"display:none\"><span property=\"description\">Winter Storm season is coming, never be stuck sitting in the dark again! With this slow burning 36 hour candle, you control how fast it burns! Each wick will burn for 12 hours if you burn all three at once you will have 12 hours of light, burn 2 wicks at once for 24 hours of light and burn each wick individually you will have 36 hours of light. Since the candle in made out of palm and soy wax you do not need to worry about chemical fumes burning off from the candle. With a compact design (2-3/8 by 3-1/8 inches)it fits cleverly into small spaces. This candle is a must for all campers, hikers, hunters, and anyone who may experience a power outage. You&#039;ll want to buy this product before you end up in the dark.</span></div>\n  <div style=\"background:#f5f5f5;padding:12px 15px;border:1px solid #e5e5e5;margin:0 0 16px\">\n    <div style=\"font-size:18px;font-weight:bold;margin-bottom:6px\">Deals Only Web Store</div>\n    <div style=\"font-size:13px\">\n      <a href=\"https://www.ebay.com/str/dealsonlywebstore\" style=\"text-decoration:none;color:#333\">Our Store</a>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n  <h2 style=\"font-size:22px;margin:0 0 12px\">ASR Outdoor 36 or 48 Hour Survival Candle for Camping Emergency Fire Starter</h2>\n  <p>Winter Storm season is coming, never be stuck sitting in the dark again!</p>\n  <h3 style=\"font-size:18px;margin:18px 0 8px\">Key Features</h3>\n  <ul style=\"padding-left:20px;margin:0 0 16px\">\n    <li><strong>INSTANT EMERGENCY LIGHT:</strong> Whether you’re hiking, camping or backpacking into the great outdoors, putting together an earthquake survival kit or struck with a blackout power outage at home, the ASR Outdoor 36 or 48 hour survival emergency light wax candle provides indoor or outdoor lighting to keep you and your family safe</li>\n    <li><strong>36 OR 48 HOUR BURN TIME:</strong> The candle’s four wick sections each have 12 hours of burn time; They can be burned all together or one at a time, providing a total 48 hours of light, using soy and regular wax; Batteries in flashlights and lanterns are expensive and can fail, while the survival candle offers a dependable indoor outdoor lighting source in any situation and can be used as a candle warmer too</li>\n    <li><strong>COMPACT LIGHTWEIGHT &amp; PORTABLE:</strong> The candle is poured in a durable tin box with lid to keep the candle in good condition; the emergency light candle fits in the palm of your hand, making it easy to pack in a bug out bag, with your camping gear or in a trekking backpack; a must-have item in any survival kit!</li>\n    <li><strong>SURVIVAL FIRE STARTER:</strong> If you have matches on hand, this candle may come in handy as a fire starter if igniting your kindling is proving troublesome; with 36 hours of burning time, getting a roaring fire started at your campsite or emergency fire in the wilderness</li>\n    <li><strong>SPECIFICATIONS:</strong> Dimensions: 2.5 x 2.5 x 2.75 inches; Surface Material: Soy wax; Main Material: Plain wax; Wax Weight: 5oz; Color: Silver, White; Total Burn Time: 36 or 48 hours; Candle is unscented</li>\n  </ul>\n  <p style=\"text-align:center;margin:0 0 16px\"><img src=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/DOWS_products/1000x1000/sports_outdoors/camping_hiking/OD-3WSC100_3wick_survival_candle_detail_06.jpg\" alt=\"Winter Storm season is coming, never be stuck sitting in the dark again\" style=\"max-width:100%;width:600px;height:auto\"></p>\n  <h3 style=\"font-size:18px;margin:18px 0 8px\">Product Specifications</h3>\n  <ul style=\"padding-left:20px;margin:0 0 16px\">\n    <li><strong>MPN:</strong> ASRO34WC</li>\n    <li><strong>UPC:</strong> 810058486592</li>\n    <li><strong>Color:</strong> White</li>\n  </ul>\n  <p>With this slow burning 36 or 48 hour candle, you control how fast it burns! Each wick will burn for 12 hours if you burn all wicks at once you will have 12 hours of light, burn 2 wicks at once for 24 hours of light and burn each wick individually you will have up to 48 hours of light.</p>\n  <p>Since the candle in made out of palm and soy wax you do not need to worry about chemical fumes burning off from the candle. With a compact design (2-3/8 by 3-1/8 inches) it fits cleverly into small spaces.</p>\n  <p>This candle is a must for all campers, hikers, hunters, and anyone who may experience a power outage. You&#039;ll want to buy this product before you end up in the dark.</p>\n  <p style=\"text-align:center;margin:16px 0 0\"><img src=\"https://s3.us-east-1.amazonaws.com/DOWS_photobucket/Shopify_Prop65graphic.jpg\" alt=\"California Proposition 65 warning\" style=\"display:block;margin-left:auto;margin-right:auto\" height=\"78\" width=\"273\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin:18px 0 0;padding-top:12px;border-top:1px solid #e5e5e5;font-size:13px;color:#777;text-align:center\">&copy; 2026 Deals Only Web Store</p>\n</div>",
